      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a pristine E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, a masterpiece of atmospheric induction with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically superlative; the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014common failure points in the S65 architecture\u2014have been proactively replaced with high-performance components. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated M Variable Differential Lock for optimal longitudinal and lateral dynamics. The chassis is free of subframe fatigue, and the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides sharp, adaptive damping. This is a turn-key enthusiast's example with zero deferred maintenance and concours-level exterior integrity.",
      "price": 44900.0,
